about_the_game: This is a clicker game where you will have to click a specific object (I won't ruin the surprise) in order to collect points, purchase upgrades and win the game. There are multiple upgrades which will allow you to increase your click power and auto clicking potential. This is a small game designed with humor in mind and is satirical in nature.

content_descriptors.notes: There is genitalia in the game.
